	剋土	insert yellow into 中;insert black into 北;insert red into 南;insert white into 西;insert green into 東	
	乘金	insert white into 西;insert green into 東;insert yellow into 中;insert black into 北;insert red into 南	
	乘木	insert green into 東;insert yellow into 中;insert black into 北;insert red into 南;insert white into 西	
